place in hand blender pot
 - 10 oz can ro-tel
 - 1/2 chopped onion
 - 2 garlic cloves
 - 1/4 tsp cumin
blend until smooth
bring to boil 
 - 1.5 cup chicken broth

set medium pot on high
add
 - 2 tbsp oil or chicken fat
 - 1 cup rice
cook until beginning to smell toasted
drain excess oil 
add tomato
cook 5 minutes
add prepared chicken stock
bring to simmer
stir 
cover
cook on low 15 minutes
stir 
cook 5 minutes
rest 10 minutes

----------------------------
 - add 19 oz drained can beans with chicken stock
 - add diced carrot with tomatoes 
 - add thawed peas in last 5 minutes of cooking 

